title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: The labels returned from the 'getcolumnlabel' method before extraction are null, while the labels returned after extraction are recognizable strings.
EB: Currently, the 'getcolumnlabel' method returns null labels before extraction. However, since these labels need to be displayed to the end user before extraction, the 'getcolumnlabel' method should return the same recognizable strings both before and after extraction.
